vernac_cmds: Lemma unrel_glb: forall a b, Share.unrel a b = Share.unrel a (Share.glb a b).
Lemma share_rel_unrel': forall r sh, Share.rel r (Share.unrel r sh) = Share.glb r sh.
Lemma share_sub_Lsh: forall sh, identity (Share.unrel Share.Rsh sh) -> join_sub sh Share.Lsh.

Lemma join_splice2_aux: forall a1 a2 a3 b1 b2 b3, Share.lub (Share.rel Share.Lsh (Share.lub a1 a2)) (Share.rel Share.Rsh (Share.lub b1 b2)) = Share.lub (Share.rel Share.Lsh a3) (Share.rel Share.Rsh b3) -> Share.lub a1 a2 = a3 /\ Share.lub b1 b2 = b3.
generalize (Share.decompose_recompose (Share.lub a1 a2, Share.lub b1 b2));intro.
Lemma share_rel_unrel: forall r sh, join_sub sh r -> Share.rel r (Share.unrel r sh) = sh.
Lemma glb_rel_Lsh_Rsh: forall a b, Share.glb (Share.rel Share.Lsh a) (Share.rel Share.Rsh b) = Share.bot.
Lemma glb_Rsh_rel_Lsh_sh: forall sh, Share.glb Share.Rsh (Share.rel Share.Lsh sh) = Share.bot.
rewrite Share.glb_commute in H1; rewrite Share.distrib1 in H1.
pose proof (Share.lub_upper1 (Share.glb b t0) (Share.glb t0 a)).
Lemma right_nonempty_readable: forall rsh sh, sepalg.nonidentity sh <-> readable_share (Share.splice rsh sh).
assert (identity sh <-> identity (Share.glb Share.Rsh (Share.lub (Share.rel Share.Lsh rsh) (Share.rel Share.Rsh sh)))); [ | intuition].
assert (identity (Share.glb (Share.rel Share.Rsh Share.top) (Share.rel Share.Rsh sh))) by (rewrite Share.rel_top1; auto).
Lemma writable_share_right: forall sh, writable_share sh -> Share.unrel Share.Rsh sh = Share.top.
Lemma unrel_bot: forall sh, nonidentity sh -> Share.unrel sh Share.bot = Share.bot.

Lemma join_splice2_aux1: forall a1 a2 b1 b2, Share.lub (Share.rel Share.Lsh (Share.glb a1 a2)) (Share.rel Share.Rsh (Share.glb b1 b2)) = Share.bot -> Share.glb a1 a2 = Share.bot /\ Share.glb b1 b2 = Share.bot.
apply lub_bot_e in H; destruct H.
Lemma join_splice: forall a1 a2 a3 b1 b2 b3, sepalg.join a1 a2 a3 -> sepalg.join b1 b2 b3 -> sepalg.join (Share.splice a1 b1) (Share.splice a2 b2) (Share.splice a3 b3).
Lemma splice_bot2: forall sh, Share.splice sh Share.bot = Share.rel Share.Lsh sh.
Lemma splice_unrel_unrel: forall sh, Share.splice (Share.unrel Share.Lsh sh) (Share.unrel Share.Rsh sh) = sh.
Lemma join_splice2: forall a1 a2 a3 b1 b2 b3 : Share.t, join (Share.splice a1 b1) (Share.splice a2 b2) (Share.splice a3 b3) -> join a1 a2 a3 /\ join b1 b2 b3.
assert ((Share.glb a1 a2 = Share.bot /\ Share.glb b1 b2 = Share.bot) /\ (Share.lub a1 a2 = a3 /\ Share.lub b1 b2 = b3)); [ | intuition].
Lemma nonidentity_rel_Lsh: forall t, nonidentity (Share.rel Share.Lsh t) -> nonidentity t.
Lemma readable_share_unrel_Rsh: forall sh, readable_share sh <-> nonunit (Share.unrel Share.Rsh sh).
